469.
1028Hetuṃ maggādhipatiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu maggādhipati dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
1029Nahetuṃ maggādhipatiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu maggādhipati dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
1030Hetuṃ maggādhipatiñca nahetuṃ maggādhipatiñca dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu maggādhipati dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
470.
1031Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe…  kamme nava, āhāre nava…pe…  avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
